summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Henry D. Kindig and Harriet Kindig, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated April 4th in the year of our Loard Nineteen Hundred Eleven (1911), to certain tracts, lots or parcels of land situate, lying and being in Section Nine (9) Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M.
